video.title: House Hunters Collection
video.synopsis: Prospective buyers and their realtors deal with both the practical and the emotional repercussions of finding and purchasing their dream home.

episodes.synopsis: An hour south of Salt Lake City, Troy and Tammy hunt for a three-bedroom, two-bath home. But while she wants a fixer-upper, he wants move-in ready.
episodes.title: Long and Quirky Wish List in Utah

episodes.synopsis: With their toddler and big dog, James and Deanna are on the hunt for a spacious home in the Seattle suburbs, but he wants new and she wants old.
episodes.title: Upgrading in the Emerald City

episodes.synopsis: Michael is ready to leave foggy San Francisco for a home in sunny Palm Springs and asks three members of The Golden Boys band to help in his search.
episodes.title: Palm Springs Paradise

episodes.synopsis: Newlyweds Jason and Emily want a vintage home in Colorado Springs's historic district, but with updated, modern conveniences and a dog-friendly yard.
episodes.title: Couple Seeks Home in Colorado

episodes.synopsis: Chicago couple Scribner and Amanda are in the market for a big house with a chicken-friendly backyard, but he wants modern and she wants charming.
episodes.title: Space for Chickens in Chicago

episodes.synopsis: Eager to buy their first home, a young couple weighs the pros and cons of three houses in suburban Atlanta: a craftsman, a colonial and a traditional.
episodes.title: Anxious to Buy in Atlanta

episodes.synopsis: NASA administrator Omar wants a huge, out-of-this-world Houston bachelor pad, complete with media and game rooms and enough yard for fruit trees.
episodes.title: Huge Home for NASA Bachelor

episodes.synopsis: Chicago interior designer Kate and husband Brandon must reconcile their conflicting wish lists and find an affordable house that works for them both.
episodes.title: Chicago Style Battle

episodes.synopsis: Craig wants a new two-story house; Katherine wants an old one-story. Can these newlyweds find a home near Dallas they can happily share?
episodes.title: Duking It Out in Dallas

episodes.synopsis: Connecticut newlyweds Alicia and Gio have different tastes in house styles, but having already rejected dozens, want to settle on a place by spring.
episodes.title: Winter Winds in Connecticut

episodes.synopsis: Recently divorced Connie wants to buy a modest house close to family in Rome, Georgia, but also wants to be near the action of the city center.
episodes.title: Fresh Start on a Tiny Budget

episodes.synopsis: Although they've never visited the Hawaiian island, a Vancouver couple shops for a vacation home on Kauai, close to the beach and with a big yard.
episodes.title: Hawaii Here We Come

episodes.synopsis: Newly engaged in Denver, Brett and Laura are anxious to end their protracted house hunt, but hit a roadblock when they can't agree on where to look.
episodes.title: Neverending House Hunt in Denver

episodes.synopsis: First-time buyers Ryan and Lydia try to reconcile conflicting desires in Phoenix. She wants a cute country home; he just wants a den and workshop.
episodes.title: Pretty or Practical in Phoenix

episodes.synopsis: Fresh to the Washington, D.C., area, Texans John and Steve experience sticker shock while shopping for a new house comparable to the ones back home.
episodes.title: Urban vs. Suburban in D.C.

episodes.synopsis: Boston renters Elisa and Stacey are eager to buy their first home. But Elisa dreams of fixing up an old house, while Stacey prefers move-in ready.
episodes.title: Looking for Opposite Things in Boston

episodes.synopsis: Tall couple Courtney and Jason have two requirements for their new home: high ceilings with plenty of headroom and proximity to downtown Tampa.
episodes.title: Too Tall in Tampa

episodes.synopsis: Although new buyers Joel and Candace both want an arty home in Little Rock, he wants a rustic fixer-upper, while she wants a modern move-in ready.
episodes.title: Woodsy vs. Modern in Arkansas

episodes.synopsis: Thriving St. Louis photographers Aaron and Heather shoot for a property that can accommodate both a professional studio and a homey living space.
episodes.title: St. Louis Cool

episodes.synopsis: Memphis newlyweds Joshua and Tracy have a long wish list for their first home that includes a music room for him and a bedroom breakfast nook for her.
episodes.title: Low Budget Blues in Memphis

episodes.synopsis: Michigan pastor Scott and wife Cindy agree they need a house upgrade. But he wants the ease of a new home while she prefers the quirks of an old one.
episodes.title: Must Be Quirky in Michigan

episodes.synopsis: In New Jersey, conflicting demands threaten to keep newly reconnected couple Gene and Erica from finding their affordable, family-friendly dream home.
episodes.title: Picky in the Garden State

episodes.synopsis: Having sold their home in Colorado, Roger and Jennifer hunt for a house in Napa Valley to realize their dream of owning a vineyard.
episodes.title: Napa Valley Dream Home

episodes.synopsis: Bryan and Chui are ready for bigger digs in Oahu's Manoa Valley, but their neighborhood's popularity has caused a major home sale shortage.
episodes.title: Honolulu House Hunt

episodes.synopsis: Eric, Kelly and their two young sons are eager to trade Eric's parents' tiny guest house for a larger, family-friendly home of their own.
episodes.title: Big House or Big Lot in Austin
